{"tid":2348041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「十，九，光，復，香，港，時，代，革，命」","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T06:48:34.000Z","uid":38610,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7d106936cff88ee404c02b33c0743d1b424463","tid":2348041,"uid":38610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmPuv3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmPuv3L.jpg&h=06918b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天琦思前想後，覺得革新同改變唔係<span class=\"red\"><strong>取決於人嘅年齡</strong></span>，而係<strong><span class=\"red\">取決於人嘅思想有冇追上時代嘅步伐</span></strong>，所以決定以「光復香港，時代革命。」作為選舉口號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dJGna8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dJGna8.png&h=5be83606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>倒數見</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68498d2916dde06b78840a01ba28ea67fcc9267","tid":2348041,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71752444d0055a64feab447eb5b245069445372","tid":2348041,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df54c1d5b031bafd585f142df5423b4f1527cdf8","tid":2348041,"uid":367280,"like":0,